* Version Control

** Conversion Mercurial (Hg) to Git using fast-export
   * Git Repo of fast-export: git://repo.or.cz/fast-export.git
   * Usage of "fast-export":
     http://hedonismbot.wordpress.com/2008/10/16/hg-fast-export-convert-mercurial-repositories-to-git-repositories/
     $ git clone git://repo.or.cz/fast-export.git
     $ mkdir new_git_repo
     $ cd new_git_repo
     $ git init
     $ /path/to/hg-fast-export.sh -r /path/to/hg_repo
     $ git checkout HEAD
